PN,36101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777389066
OL,3,C75 pupils swap smartphones for
OL,4,C'bricks' for three weeks
OL,6,FPupils at five schools in Sheffield
OL,7,Fare giving up smartphones in a three-
OL,8,Fweek project exploring the impact of
OL,9,Fscreen time.
OL,11,FThe 75 seven to 16-year-olds will swap
OL,12,Ftheir devices for basic "brick" phones
OL,13,Fto stay in contact with family and
OL,14,Ffriends while avoiding social media.
OL,16,FEleven-year-old Spencer Kubon, who
OL,17,Fattends Lound Juniors, said he was
OL,18,Flooking forward to "not going on the
OL,19,Fphone when bored, do more stuff around
OL,20,Fthe house and getting outside more".
OL,26,@tD@YOUtD@_O]
