FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777389066
OL,3,C75 pupils swap smartphones for
OL,4,C'bricks' for three weeks
OL,6,FStanley Sheldon 13, from Ecclesfield
OL,7,FSecondary School, says he might
OL,8,Fstruggle, adding: "I am a little
OL,9,Fanxious bit I am up for it. I will
OL,10,Fhave to just deal with it if I find it
OL,11,Fhard, but most people doing this will
OL,12,Ffind freedom from it."
OL,14,FHeavy phone usage is widely thought to
OL,15,Fcontribute to sleep problems, low
OL,16,Fconcentration, reduced physical
OL,17,Factivity and social withdrawal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
