OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777389066
OL,3,C75 pupils swap smartphones for
OL,4,C'bricks' for three weeks
OL,6,FNational figures from Ofcom suggest
OL,7,Fnearly all children spend time online,
OL,8,Fwith most owning a mobile phone by the
OL,9,Fage of 11.
OL,11,FThe S35 Unplugged project is being led
OL,12,Fby Ecclesfield, along with four local
OL,13,Fprimary schools, and follows a scheme
OL,14,Flast year which saw Sheffield Hallam
OL,15,FUniversity research the impact on 32
OL,16,Fpupils who gave up their smart phones
OL,17,Ffor three months.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777389066
OL,3,C75 pupils swap smartphones for
OL,4,C'bricks' for three weeks
OL,6,FEcclesfield teacher Liz Hunter said,
OL,7,F"Not only did the project show the
OL,8,Fpupils what life is like without their
OL,9,Fphones, they reported so many
OL,10,Fpositives of having the break from
OL,11,Flife online, like less anxiety and
OL,12,Fbetter friendships.
OL,14,F"A number of them were quite upset
OL,15,Fabout getting their phones back at the
OL,16,Fend of the project because they'd
OL,17,Ffound their time without them so
OL,18,Fliberating."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
