OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777389066
OL,3,C75 pupils swap smartphones for
OL,4,C'bricks' for three weeks
OL,6,FHeadteacher Richard Walkden added: "We
OL,7,Fsaw that students were happier,
OL,8,Fconcentrated more on their work, spent
OL,9,Ftime with family and also spent time
OL,10,Fdeveloping skills like fishing, guitar
OL,11,For woodwork".
OL,13,FPupil Isobel Phillips, 15, who is
OL,14,Ftaking part for a second time, said:
OL,15,F"Because we're raised on
OL,16,F(smartphones), it's really eye-opening
OL,17,Fto see how it was before them and to
OL,18,Fbe more simple".
OL,26,@xD@ApmxD@Mpn
